---
title: Sizzling Korean Beef with Bok Choy
description: This dish is all about crispy, sizzling beef strips sprinkled with the nuttiness of sesame seeds. A scorching hot surface is what your steak needs to add a perfect smokiness to all that lovely flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sizzling-korean-beef-26dcad88.jpg
